  "detailed_description": "Let's vanish some ghosts! Shoot, run, throw grenades, explore indoor places, have some fun and get a little scared.<br><br>In this action game you will be hired to terminate all the ghosts from haunted places. You will be equipped with different kinds of special anti-ghost weapons. Listen carefully to detect any ghosts that might be getting close to you, otherwise you're dead!<br><br>Earn Ghost Points while killing ghosts to buy more weapons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751850/extras/404a4341e7315985df57a2b7edb0e580.poster.avif?t=1730553678\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751850/extras/404a4341e7315985df57a2b7edb0e580.webm?t=1730553678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751850/extras/404a4341e7315985df57a2b7edb0e580.mp4?t=1730553678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751850/extras/cb825753cf862bca4931d8168e23c121.avif?t=1730553678\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751850/extras/3e4141f130c0a012611361d2dd3ac2a4.poster.avif?t=1730553678\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751850/extras/3e4141f130c0a012611361d2dd3ac2a4.webm?t=1730553678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751850/extras/3e4141f130c0a012611361d2dd3ac2a4.mp4?t=1730553678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video cla